# Appalachian Archives Mobile

A React Native app built with Expo for browsing and playing digitized video archives. Designed for use with Expo Go and optimized for mobile playback.

## ðŸ“¦ Tech Stack

- [Expo](https://expo.dev/) (managed workflow)
- React Native + TypeScript
- `expo-av` for native video playback
- React Navigation (stack-based)
- Metro bundler for local development

## ðŸš€ Getting Started

### 1. Clone the repo

```bash
git clone https://github.com/YOUR_USERNAME/appalachian-archives-mobile.git
cd appalachian-archives-mobile

Install Dependencies
npm install
# or
yarn install

Start the development server
npx expo start

