Features
Browse a list of digitized videos
Tap to play videos using native controls
Works in Expo Go and on physical Android devices
Type-safe navigation and props

Development Notes
Video playback uses expo-av, not react-native-video
Metro cache may need to be cleared after dependency changes:
npx expo start -c

Emulator port forwarding
adb reverse tcp:8081 tcp:8081

